    public class AnInsertReq
extends AnUpdateReq

    Insert Request helper

    Note:

    AnInsertReq is a subclass of AnUpdateReq.

    Because all request element is deserialized as an AnUpdateReq, so this can only work for Update/Insert request.

    Author:
    odys-z@github.com
